org.gvsig.fmap.dal.coverage.grid

Interface RegistrableFilterListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConvolutionUI, MaskUI, RegionAlphaUI

    public interface RegistrableFilterListener
    Each panel of a filter should implement this interface. It provides methods for add and remove listeners and get the parameters.
